item.title: CVE-2017-20133|2024-08-05T21:45:25.984Z -- itech -- job%20portal%20script
item.description: A vulnerability, which was classified as critical, was found in Itech Job Portal Script 9.13. This affects an unknown part of the file /admin. The manipulation leads to improper authentication. It is possible to initiate the attack remotely.
